Lindroth, 1968: 801. Type locality: &quot;7-15 mi[les] N[orth] of New Rampart House, Alaska&quot; (original citation). Holotype (â™‚) in USNM [# 75705]. Note. New Rampart House was a trading post on the Porcupine River in Yukon Territory near the border with Alaska.
</paragraph>
